{"tid":2351040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線「新」中國組 狂引央視報道  招牌獨家古無影 前記者：慘不忍睹","createTime":"2021-01-03T00:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T03:23:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f85e7217a20a11f25f6a8e725994d6e6c330d9c5","tid":2351040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210103/LZEVJ2LRONARNL6YNUIZJ3F5IE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210103%2FLZEVJ2LRONARNL6YNUIZJ3F5IE%2F&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=bda21fcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210103%2FLZEVJ2LRONARNL6YNUIZJ3F5IE%2F&h=885b3827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210103/LZEVJ2LRONARNL6YNUIZJ3F5IE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有線「新」中國組 狂引央視報道 <br />\n招牌獨家古無影 前記者：慘不忍睹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J49HwbU3Bj2O_vFAa6kNAUONBHA=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NU7GBUFPHRFKLM7NBQDEZAQAXI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ49HwbU3Bj2O_vFAa6kNAUONBHA%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNU7GBUFPHRFKLM7NBQDEZAQAXI.jpg&h=c1a48a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有線新聞中國組在元旦日以新班底登場 （圖），即以央視關於固體廢物的報道（下圖）作為頭條。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼CCTVB後，香港又有一家CableCCTV獻世。有線新聞中國組全體總辭後，「新」中國組元旦登場，但有觀眾發現，15分鐘節目播出七條兩岸新聞，有三條均是內地官媒央視（CCTV）專題報道，其中「內地元旦日起禁止進口固體廢物」更放在頭條播出，有線中國組昔日招牌的獨家古就無影。有前有線新聞中國組記者形容「慘不忍睹，好心痛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nTvn3_NwcAIy2eCL8b6uXhHZOqo=/1000x561/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZHWQTQT4NC6XGKPV6VUKTVNLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnTvn3_NwcAIy2eCL8b6uXhHZOqo%3D%2F1000x561%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZHWQTQT4NC6XGKPV6VUKTVNLM.jpg&h=70f670b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■央視關於固體廢物的報道。<br />\n<br />\n該名有線中國組前記者向本報指，。。。。。。。。。。。，「真係寧願唔播好過」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查前日有線新聞「新」中國組節目，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呂秉權：官方喉舌難反映真相<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞部上月大地震，管理層未有諮詢各組別主管就裁員40人，其中生招牌中國組一人被炒，觸發全組記者和主管總辭。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原屬有線新聞國際組的張偉聰，臨危受命調任中國組，新一年首日報道七宗新聞，有六宗都是由他旁述，至於負責撰稿的宋啟春，據稱是新聘請員工，以普通話為母語。<br />\n<br />\n有線中國組前首席記者、浸大新聞系高級講師呂秉權指，央視新聞是官方喉舌，無法恰如其分反映民間真相，甚至中央領導人等都會認為，官媒只寫「官樣文章」，水份甚多，只能作宣傳工作及塑造形象之用，不足以反映真相。"},{"pid":"e570c50b460d03a2441d788c81f3783c059d77ae","tid":2351040,"uid":205937,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"依加有線中国組成浸TVB味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同CCTVB一樣將台灣當做中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49208e83d58780e71cb714c4174420199c98f81","tid":2351040,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"預咗啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb20c4755b70a126d12a964aff4981c1dc8d4bc","tid":2351040,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"比錢睇央視？<br />\n步亞視後塵啦<br />\ncut 得"},{"pid":"011446f36f7e80892f2af73883f024d7a4b4f0a6","tid":2351040,"uid":304856,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9856227fda4d9611e53e67233369db1aebac8813","tid":2351040,"uid":272271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"整個fb challenge <br />\n每人tag 最少5個like左中國組page嘅friends，被tag中就要unlike個page再傳出去"},{"pid":"110c5046e091b20935ad3f734efd5fa299096085","tid":2351040,"uid":102554,"like":0,"